Sweden Load Dashboard

Interactive charts generated from ENTSO-E data

Actual Load Notes

Actual Total Load

Measured total load each hour for SE.

Notes

  • Times are displayed in Europe/Stockholm.
  • A load for a specific hour indicates the average load during a one hour period. As an example, the data point at 15:00 indicates the load between 15:00-16:00.
  • Data source: ENTSO-E (Actual Total Load for SE).
Built with Python + Plotly, deployed on GitHub Pages.
